Interface Printable

All Known Implementing Classes:
BankStatement, Customer
public interface Printable
Instructor: Daniel Mejia, Course: CS 3331 Lab Assignment: Programming Assignment 4 Description: The purpose of the interface Printable is to define the methods to be used for printing a bank customer's account/transaction information to the console or to a file. Honesty Statement: We confirm that the work of this assignment is completely our own. By turning in this assignment, we declare that we did not receive unauthorized assistance. Moreover, all deliverables including, but not limited to the source code, lab report, and output files were written and produced by my partner and I, alone.
